---
const basePath = import.meta.env.PROD ? '/Genesis/' : '/';
---

<title>Meet The Genesis Team</title>

<div class="mt-32 mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8" id="leadership">
    <div class="text-center">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-gray-900 mb-12">Our Leadership Team</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
        <!-- Alan Michaels - CEO -->
        <div class="text-center">
            <img src=`${basePath}Img/brent.jpg` alt="Alan Michaels" class="mx-auto rounded-full w-80 h-80 object-cover shadow-xl transition-transform transform hover:scale-110 hover:shadow-3xl"/>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mt-6">Alan Michaels - CEO</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Alan Michaels is a graduate of MIT, where he studied Mechanical Engineering. An expert in aerospace technology, Alan directed crucial engineering projects before joining Genesis. His strategic vision and passion for marrying engineering with emerging tech have driven significant growth and innovation at Genesis, solidifying our market leadership.</p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Brian Matthews - CFO -->
        <div class="text-center">
            <img src=`${basePath}Img/ian.jpg` alt="Brian Matthews" class="mx-auto rounded-full w-80 h-80 object-cover shadow-xl transition-transform transform hover:scale-110 hover:shadow-3xl"/>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mt-6">Brian Matthews - CFO</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Brian Matthews, with a finance background from the University of Illinois, brings extensive experience from working at a top competitor. As CFO, he has restructured Genesis's financial operations to enhance profitability and sustainability, playing a crucial role in strengthening our global competitive stance and capital management.</p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Elizabeth Redding - CTO -->
        <div class="text-center">
            <img src=`${basePath}Img/caroline.jpg` alt="Abby Smith" class="mx-auto rounded-full w-80 h-80 object-cover shadow-xl transition-transform transform hover:scale-110 hover:shadow-3xl"/>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mt-6">Elizabeth Redding - CTO</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Elizabeth Redding holds a degree in Computer Science from Stanford University. Her career began in Silicon Valley, developing innovative software solutions. At Genesis, she has led the adoption of advanced computational tools that enhance our design and manufacturing processes, establishing us as technology leaders in our industry.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Abby Smith - Chief Design Engineer -->
        <div class="text-center">
            <img src=`${basePath}Img/PeopleGenesis/person8.jpg` alt="Abby Smith" class="mx-auto rounded-full w-80 h-80 object-cover shadow-xl transition-transform transform hover:scale-110 hover:shadow-3xl"/>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mt-6">Abby Smith - Chief Design Engineer</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Abby Smith, an acclaimed design engineer, graduated from the University of Michigan with a degree in Mechanical Engineering. She has a remarkable track record in leading innovative design projects across multiple sectors, including aerospace and automotive. At Genesis, Abby is responsible for setting the strategic design direction worldwide, integrating cutting-edge technologies to enhance product aesthetics and functionality across global markets.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Fred Reed - Global Head of Product Development Engineering -->
        <div class="text-center">
            <img src=`${basePath}Img/PeopleGenesis/person1.jpg` alt="Abby Smith" class="mx-auto rounded-full w-80 h-80 object-cover shadow-xl transition-transform transform hover:scale-110 hover:shadow-3xl"/>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mt-6">Fred Reed - Global Head of Product Development Engineering</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Fred Reed holds a degree in Industrial Engineering from Purdue University and has extensive experience developing pioneering products in the consumer electronics industry. Known for his innovative approach, Fred leads Genesis's product development engineering on a global scale, focusing on creating breakthrough products that resonate with emerging market trends and customer needs.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Jan Wilcox - Global Director of Manufacturing Engineering -->
        <div class="text-center">
            <img src=`${basePath}Img/PeopleGenesis/person6.jpg` alt="Abby Smith" class="mx-auto rounded-full w-80 h-80 object-cover shadow-xl transition-transform transform hover:scale-110 hover:shadow-3xl"/>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mt-6">Jan Wilcox - Global Director of Manufacturing Engineering</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Jan Wilcox earned her degree in Manufacturing Engineering from Georgia Tech and is renowned for optimizing complex production processes. With her expertise in lean manufacturing and process automation, Jan oversees Genesis's manufacturing engineering efforts globally, constantly seeking improvements in efficiency and quality to maintain the company's competitive edge.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Victor Viola - Global VP of Strategic Sales -->
        <div class="text-center">
            <img src=`${basePath}Img/PeopleGenesis/person2.jpg` alt="Abby Smith" class="mx-auto rounded-full w-80 h-80 object-cover shadow-xl transition-transform transform hover:scale-110 hover:shadow-3xl"/>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mt-6">Victor Viola - Global VP of Strategic Sales</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Victor Viola, a Sales Executive with a degree in Business Administration from Harvard Business School, has an impressive background in driving sales growth in multinational corporations. Since joining Genesis, Victor has spearheaded the strategic sales initiatives that have empowered Genesis to penetrate new markets and secure vital OEM partnerships, ensuring sustained revenue growth.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

